# The committed knowledge-graph map merges by graph union: the
# [merge "graphify-union"] driver defined in the user gitconfig
# (dot_gitconfig.tmpl) runs `graphify merge-driver`. Where the driver is not
# configured (CI, other machines), git falls back to a normal merge conflict,
# resolvable by regenerating the map (`graphify update .`).
graphify-out/graph.json merge=graphify-union
